            <h2>‚ùå The Problem: Without Services</h2>
            
            <div class="problem-text">
                <strong>Scenario:</strong> You deploy an application using a Deployment that creates 3 pod replicas. Users access pods directly via IP addresses.
            </div>
            
            <div class="diagram">
